Include #include "Chaos/Collision/ParticlePairMidPhase.h"

Syntax

class FParticlePairMidPhase

Remarks

The lifetime of midphase objects is handled entirely by the CollisionConstraintAllocator. Nothing outside of the CollisionConstraintAllocator should hold a pointer to the detector or any constraints it creates for more than the duration of the tick.

description: Produce collisions for a particle pair A [FParticlePairMidPhase](API\Runtime\Chaos\Chaos\Collision\FParticlePairMidPhase) object is created for every particle pair whose bounds overlap. It is responsible for building a set of potentially colliding shape pairs and running collision detection on those pairs each tick.
